{"tid":1001044,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有無D唔洗應酬同事同老細既工作","createTime":"2019-01-30T00:31:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-14T04:17:29.000Z","uid":119908,"like":44,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"db123a751cdce577bc745e5f1172c3a58d630e5f","tid":1001044,"uid":119908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T00:31:23.000Z","msg":"覺得日日要扮自己好hyper好energetic好攰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個工作環境既文化係同事們都懶friend呀 一得閒就成日吹水呀個種<br />\n點解會知係懶friend呢 因為從言語間係聽得出佢地其實唔熟<br />\n但其實我份人好慢熱 又唔識開話題<br />\n一得閒只會想禁下電話同朋友whatsapp或者睇下facebook<br />\n對同事既生活真心無咩興趣<br />\n但基於呢個文化 我就要日日都要假笑咁返工 逼自己周圍聊人去social<br />\n<br />\n係咪我唔適合呢份工 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定我唔適合係呢個社會生存 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我成日係度諗 返工係咪就係唔可以做返自己<br />\n要活成另一個自己<br />\n呢D先叫成長<br />\n<br />\n老細響我返工第一日就同我講<br />\n你讀書唔夠叻 就係注定要做人地妹仔<br />\n唉 駁唔到<br />\n大家話我可以點做 <br />\n而家又要搭車返工了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fca516df1e24febe29e1a4ba96b7ffcd6f997855","tid":1001044,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T00:38:57.000Z","msg":"咩工先"},{"pid":"23ab57ed061df19e15d135709e76b62c66834d52","tid":1001044,"uid":226562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T00:41:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ddd36ae8743d1339f770e99b14515ebec2bd2ff5","tid":1001044,"uid":119908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fca516df1e24febe29e1a4ba96b7ffcd6f997855","tid":1001044,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T00:38:57.000Z","msg":"咩工先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T00:56:12.000Z","msg":"對人多過對電腦既工作 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbe69825a8762f3a326d137c3d643b3ff9be3eb3","tid":1001044,"uid":119908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23ab57ed061df19e