 />\n而係希望對方唔好踩你一腳<br />\n<br />\n對上司 唔係希望對方可以賞識自己<br />\n而係希望對方唔好成日餵自己食屎<br />\n<br />\n對老細 唔係希望對方可以提攜自己 升職加薪<br />\n而係希望對方有一個唔差印象<br />\n<br />\n好老實 幾時都講 <br />\n識人好過識字<br />\n識做人好過識做野<br />\n<br />\n你做到識飛又有乜野用<br />\n都不及擦鞋仔一盒鞋油<br />\n當然擦鞋都唔係一樣簡單技能<br />\n但係只係識得認真工作 真係好蝕底"},{"pid":"a4138df68873565dbdcead152c30ce2c47ad73f4","tid":1001044,"uid":84040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6fa35b3ba461611e741cabbb9661864430974f7","tid":1001044,"uid":119908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4786aa2f29c4a0879660caee74cc549c2a0523df","tid":1001044,"uid":84040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e583982c6e9af8681004dcbead7bf91afcfe8b33","tid":1001044,"uid":119908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T01:11:05.000Z","msg":"我都想有能力可以做到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真心羨慕it狗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T10:50:03.000Z","msg":"羨慕隻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申it狗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T13:05:00.000Z","msg":"有無少少自豪 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T16:24:27.000Z","msg":"做狗有乜好自豪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd5255a144abc0e481cead227693d6b01d03896c","tid":1001044,"uid":119908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2172711c937a7a6d7cee202289b163f0bdfc29f9","tid":1001044,"uid":193131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T13:11:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我做補習社，唔需要同其他同事social<br />\n做好自己本份就夠"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T00:29:51.000Z","msg":"得閒既時候都唔洗吹水咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好好呀"},{"pid":"c014e94664424259a8ad073acc7a0e8a145ae377","tid":1001044,"uid":119908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9fae