覺得自己成為緊以前細個好討厭既個種人"},{"pid":"64204b25b0fff531d14464818d7ef30f0b4f2b09","tid":1001044,"uid":216704,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c014e94664424259a8ad073acc7a0e8a145ae377","tid":1001044,"uid":119908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9faeec528551e3cac0cb4cda84875afef6725e98","tid":1001044,"uid":218954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9681ddc8de4f55b7fe1dfe18ef0a0e784f58ffd","tid":1001044,"uid":119908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T13:04:39.000Z","msg":"我都想！做咩生意好"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T13:17:53.000Z","msg":"做生意先最需要social呀<br />\n我都想打份唔洗social嘅工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時最攰唔係做嘢<br />\n而係要戴住假面具對同事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T00:31:10.000Z","msg":"So true <br />\n明明心情唔好既日子<br />\n都要捧住面具做人<br />\n到底是為了什麼 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T01:28:51.000Z","msg":"最慘係明知班人 係背後成日講你壞話<br />\n都仲要扮冇野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db549876093a4ec5511dfcda71214f508a7edca2","tid":1001044,"uid":119330,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"64204b25b0fff531d14464818d7ef30f0b4f2b09","tid":1001044,"uid":216704,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c014e94664424259a8ad073acc7a0e8a145ae377","tid":1001044,"uid":119908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9faeec528551e3cac0cb4cda84875afef6725e98","tid":1001044,"uid":218954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T13:17:53.000Z","msg":"做生意先最需要social呀<br />\n我都想打份唔洗social嘅工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時最攰唔係做嘢<br />\n而係要戴住假面具對同事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"cited